Description:
This workout split will have lots of variety where the user trains different muscle groups every day. It is organized so that each day the user trains at least one large muscle group, ex: chest, and one smaller muscle group ex: biceps. 

No equipment, beginner routine:

Chest and Biceps:
  Pushups
  Bicep Pushups
Quads and  calves:
  Bodyweight squats
  Standing Calf Raises
Back and Triceps
  Alternating Bringbacks
  Diamond Pushups
Hamstrings and shoulders:
  Good mornings
  Pike Pushups

Access to pullup Bar beginner routine :

Chest and Biceps:
  Pushups
  Chinups
Quads and  calves:
  Bodyweight squats
  Standing calf raises
Back and Triceps
  Pullups
  Diamond Pushups
Hamstrings and shoulders:
  Goodmornings
  Pike pushups

Access to dumbells beginner routine
Chest and Biceps:
  Pushups 
  Dumbell Bicep curls
Quads and  calves:
